    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rune it Out is a multiplayer PVP game but you can also play with AI.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the game, you combine different runes to cast spells that will change the map and turn your friends to dust.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A great dwarven Smith was born in a magical world. He was so skilled in smithing that he felt limited by physical means alone. To surpass these limitations, he incorporated magic into his craft and invented a new object called a rune. By combining runes, he developed a new method of casting magic, which he called &quot;Rune Casting.&quot; Soon after, an arena was built where the most skilled &quot;Rune mages&quot; competed for fame and mana. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213910/extras/8ff35e93fd30ef93c378b58e155fe39a.avif?t=1728827922\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213910/extras_big/8ff35e93fd30ef93c378b58e155fe39a.avif?t=1728827922 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer and Singleplayer(AI)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple character choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine Different runes to create amazing spells</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully Interactive map</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Progressing Grimoire (Spell Book)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill other &quot;Rune Mages&quot; to gain their &quot;rune mana&quot; and use it to unlock new spells in a grimoire</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213910/extras/eadae92ab1295102b31b25d408a96d76.avif?t=1728827922\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213910/extras_big/eadae92ab1295102b31b25d408a96d76.avif?t=1728827922 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >- Chanting </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Type your spells as fast as you can. Otherwise, your RuneMage also won't chant them fast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213910/extras/2c59e7c79330bb5497b60ae8c99b4e2d.avif?t=1728827922\" width=700 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Miscasting :</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Concentrate on casting your spells. If you don't, you will miscast them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Artefact Mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not long after, a new competition the &quot;Artefact Battle&quot; was invented, one in which multiple &quot;Rune Mages&quot; clashed their spells against each other to attain an Artefact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213910/extras/da650fa0e85f3eaab4324b4a9f40b990.avif?t=1728827922\" width=500 height=176 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Clashing spells: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to counter the enemy spells as fast as possible</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Multiplayer PvP </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Mana:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Counter, the spells of your enemies or hit them with your own to acquire mana and Achieve Victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
